data.description: Double-wide 3 BE/2 full BA manufactured home located on a large private fully fenced lot on a dead-end road. NEW ROOF! Open split bedroom floor plan, with large rooms, vaulted ceilings, double-sink vanity and a garden tub in the master suite. The kitchen offers generous storage, pass-thru window and a breakfast bar. There is a separate INSIDE laundry area with a full washer and dryer and a detached shed for extra storage. You will love the large, level, tranquil lot. Only minutes away from Jennings State Forest. Chirping birds are included and animals are welcomed too!
